{"tid":6213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左十年澳門賭場電視房 你問我答","createTime":"2016-11-27T08:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T04:33:58.000Z","uid":28377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a201c1c72c4828064250961ae106daa34082fde0","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6dc5cf11f05f3c0686bff4e4fd510d306297c7","tid":6213,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"點睇澳門首家線上賭場上線啦"},{"pid":"96e9b383b30834d3c5d15d966ad9928c719cbb1c","tid":6213,"uid":8177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"最難忘嘅是係乜"},{"pid":"9f88cbe56d4ed6fa7077a3ba6a1a05ea385e373f","tid":6213,"uid":8177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最難忘嘅是係乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用voice輸入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af70dd1c3573ee742e4a6f4f2c85256af1e696b5","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇澳門首家線上賭場上線啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n非法網站 絕對係一個大騙局 相信有一定用戶後就會走佬關網頁 之後再開個新既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6be7bb60283091f60f34b9e4170b8e42815d5d","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最難忘嘅是係乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有兩單好難忘 一單係跳樓睇慢境時 個客應該係半空中就死左 因為佢全身都硬曬 另一單係斬人 見住隻手指飛出黎感覺好震撼 同睇戲好唔同"},{"pid":"2b9f048d590a2aa78b465c384f7c5e893e8a8949","tid":6213,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"捉到老千，佢會點？"},{"pid":"cad66da0c488b341fc6b00b5658083166559fe13","tid":6213,"uid":5424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:19:26.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb909c7b4da3661e23345303aa536a07c2ccca32","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉到老千，佢會點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇佢偷幾錢 小金額既會的佢入一間房困佢幾個鐘 之後放走 大金額可能會直接去司法 但老千其實都分好多種 所以好難講清楚曬"},{"pid":"3e62c862302a671d9c50cb79b11e971713e739d4","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咩職位 新仔就15000-18000 唔同賭場唔同價"},{"pid":"3a0efc9df81ba6de1c8d98f9848a86ddfd711d90","tid":6213,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36a374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36a374.jpg&h=73553980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3341c015bc0d45ec8941401ecebd2dbd9892c1a","tid":6213,"uid":10774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"見過/聽過係普通枱一晚贏最多個客贏幾多"},{"pid":"8c8aef9bae1b28ec28260828a2ed91e5dbf85f8d","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://na.cx/i/36a374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36a374.jpg&h=f58ec51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好信呢d低能野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就係會有電子儀器 但唔係睇呢d 有種係專門計百家樂對子既出現率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135298fce2164018ef0d1156275239c43b3dbc97","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過/聽過係普通枱一晚贏最多個客贏幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通枱其實真係賭得好細 我記憶中唔超過一千萬好似最多700-800萬"},{"pid":"1f9179b3b65efff7e51af7244b07e510fe3762c9","tid":6213,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見過/聽過係普通枱一晚贏最多個客贏幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通枱其實真係賭得好細 我記憶中唔超過一千萬好似最多700-800萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁貴賓室一晚咪贏成億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e92ddec36d68bce438e13d54937234c82b4c24","tid":6213,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"份工點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e4f1f74590ce25df143eae3d32820295a64d88","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見過/聽過係普通枱一晚贏最多個客贏幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通枱其實真係賭得好細 我記憶中唔超過一千萬好似最多700-800萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁貴賓室一晚咪贏成億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多好似八千幾萬 聽聞個客有養鬼仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d77d9915789d6f3ab9ffbe0e70c3a5379f96e7","tid":6213,"uid":28377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>份工點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上官網 成日請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34719c834d8d151bcd84144746028b909ab2cdbe","tid":6213,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>份工點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上官網 成日請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁請問個職位叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b4564d9c0ad2146233d27f94ebb2a1bb90026e","tid":6213,"uid":28270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>份工點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上官網 成日請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁請問個職位叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n監控控制員<br />\n樓主叫得電視房係 STDM,SJM 叫， E 家好少人咁叫，所以我信樓主做緊冇鳩吹"},{"pid":"9cd4b7ac434c3c99c3264775bbb5958b16e1651f","tid":6213,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>份工點申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上官網 成日請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁請問個職位叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.